Tools based on MINERvA Software
https://minerva.fnal.gov
No comercial purposes

*******
1) Change setup.csh or setup.sh according to your directory path
  JOYROOT = your JoyRoot Path
2) change on src/Makefile for
Mac os x:
  LDFLAGS += -shared -Wl,-install_name
Linux gcc 4.6
  DFLAGS += -shared -Wl,-soname
3) To run scripts/makeAnaSkeleton.py, running outside JoyRoot directory
  i.e.
  cd $HOME
  source JoyRoot/scripts/makeAnaSkeleton.py <worpath> <dirname> <classname>
************

To use any function we should call like static tootl
Plot1::bookTH1F(******)
instead of
Plot1 *p1;
p1->bookTH1F(*****);

